fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "gtkcontainer-h.html#gtk_container_set_focus_hadjustment", "fragment": "gtk_container_set_focus_hadjustment \nGtk.prototype.set_focus_hadjustment \nGtk.Container.set_focus_hadjustment \nHooks up an adjustment to focus handling in a container so when a child of the container is focused the adjustment is scrolled to show that widget. This function sets the horizontal alignment. See gtk_scrolled_window_get_hadjustment for a typical way of obtaining the adjustment and gtk_container_set_focus_vadjustment for setting the vertical adjustment. \nThe adjustments have to be in pixel units and in the same coordinate system as the allocation for immediate children of the container. \nParameters \na GtkContainer \nan adjustment which should be adjusted when the focus is moved among the descendents of container \nHooks up an adjustment to focus handling in a container so when a child of the container is focused the adjustment is scrolled to show that widget. This function sets the horizontal alignment. See Gtk.prototype.get_hadjustment for a typical way of obtaining the adjustment and Gtk.prototype.set_focus_vadjustment for setting the vertical adjustment. \nThe adjustments have to be in pixel units and in the same coordinate system as the allocation for immediate children of the container. \nParameters \na Gtk.Container \nan adjustment which should be adjusted when the focus is moved among the descendents of container \nHooks up an adjustment to focus handling in a container so when a child of the container is focused the adjustment is scrolled to show that widget. This function sets the horizontal alignment. See Gtk.ScrolledWindow.get_hadjustment for a typical way of obtaining the adjustment and Gtk.Container.set_focus_vadjustment for setting the vertical adjustment. \nThe adjustments have to be in pixel units and in the same coordinate system as the allocation for immediate children of the container. \nParameters \na Gtk.Container \nan adjustment which should be adjusted when the focus is moved among the descendents of container \n"});